Getting Input from the User
-------------------------------
     Using Text Fields
     -----------------
     :: A text field is a box into which the user can type a single line of text.
     :: You create text fields by using the TextField class.
                ***RolePlayer.java***

      Validating Numeric Data
     ------------------------
        :: The getText method returns a string value
        :: Use the parseInt() method to convert the value entered in a text box to an int
                    Integer parseInt(String)
                    Short parseShort(String)
                    Long parseLong(String)
                    Byte parseByte(String)
                    Float parseFloat(String)
                    Double parseDouble(String)
        :: If your program uses more than one or two numeric-entry text fields, consider creating separate methods to validate the userâ€™s input.
                    ***RolePlayer.java***

